ranslated as Disaster Recovery Plan, DRP. This is known as a set of actions and human, technical and procedural resources that serve to recover, in the minimum time and at the lowest cost, an interrupted activity within a company due to an emergency. <\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The classification society Bureau Veritas suffered a cyber-attack on November 20 that forced it to temporarily shut down its servers and data systems.\u00a0 This is a preventive action it has had to take to protect its customers while investigations are carried out and appropriate measures are taken. As a result, customers may have experienced a &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/msiamericas.com\/industrial-cybersecurity-startup-claroty-raises-140m-in-pre-ipo-funding-round-2\/\"> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Bureau Veritas suffers cyber attack<\/span> Read More &raquo;<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":16462,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"default","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"","footer-sml-layout":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[],"acf":[],"lang":false,"translations":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/msiamericas.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6072"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/msiamericas.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/msiamericas.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/msiamericas.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/6"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"h